[
    {
        "content": "<p>I can't find any documentation on how to use cranelift backend. I've enabled it in config.toml. How do I make rustc use it instead of LLVM?</p>",
        "id": 226232587,
        "sender_full_name": "osa1",
        "timestamp": 1613202166
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>change <code>codegen-backends=[\"llvm\"]</code> in your <code>config.toml</code></p>",
        "id": 226232666,
        "sender_full_name": "oliver",
        "timestamp": 1613202357
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>As I said, I already enabled it in config.toml. I currently have both LLVM and cranelift enabled.</p>",
        "id": 226232713,
        "sender_full_name": "osa1",
        "timestamp": 1613202404
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>or <code>-Zcodegen-backend=cranelift</code> then</p>",
        "id": 226232803,
        "sender_full_name": "oliver",
        "timestamp": 1613202589
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Perfect, thanks</p>",
        "id": 226232877,
        "sender_full_name": "osa1",
        "timestamp": 1613202697
    },
